Because Ladies & Gentlemen matches my prioritized attributes (intimate vocals, transparent/dynamic mastering, midrange instrumentation, restraint and thoughtful sequencing) while the High‑energy AOR/pop disc directly embodies the characteristics I dislike (compressed, rhythm‑first mixes, reduced nuance, singles‑first sequencing), Ladies & Gentlemen: The Best of George Michael is the clear fit.

